body.description: The 3-in-1 backpack design makes it easy to cross your body for hand-free carry, and also it comes with a tote design, and you can use it as a handbag, or shoulder bag too. Features: 1. For babies 0-12 months old. When the baby grows up, the changing station can be separated and the diaper bag can be used as an ordinary backpack. 2. Storage - This spacious diaper bag offers plenty of storage to fit all of your mum (or dad) essentials for your baby girl or boy (or even twins!) 3. Material - Lightweight, durable and waterproof fabric (Stronger & Better in Deform Resistance & Tear Resistance) 4.Durable But Lightweight - Our diaper backpack is made of lightweight, durable and waterproof fabric. Non-fraying stitching, and strong zippers. Reinforced seams in shoulder straps and handle, without ripping. 5. No need to assemble. 6. Easy to clean, breathable removable mesh material and a sheet of the pad is machine-washable. Note: 1. Please remove the pad cover and wash it before use. 2. Do not clean the inner core of the pad. Vacuum cotton cloth may shrink after cleaning. Please expose the inner core directly to the sun. 3. Please allow 1-2in differences due to manual measurement. Your satisfaction is always our pursuit, please connect us if you have any questions about our product.
